         (* ;; "Search more broadly for PROP before asking--comes after CANDIDATE because it could be an HCFILES default. BFILE's directory has priority")

              (CL:WHEN [AND PROP (SETQ USER.CM (OR (LISTP PROP)
                                                   (FINDFILE PROP T DIRS]
